---
---

<section id="about" class="bg-black-950 py-24">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">

      <!-- Text -->
      <div>
        <p class="text-brass-500 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-4">We're Here to Serve You</p>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white-100 leading-tight mb-6">
          Do More of What You Love.<br />And Less of What You Don't.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-white-200/65 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-10">
          You started this business because you're passionate about what you do — not because you wanted to spend your evenings figuring out social media, ad campaigns, and content strategy. We step in so you don't have to. From digital presence to full marketing execution, we handle it all while you stay focused on what actually moves the needle for you.
        </p>

        <ul class="space-y-7 mb-10">

          <!-- Camera icon -->
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="mt-0.5 w-10 h-10 rounded-sm bg-brass-500/10 border border-brass-500/30 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brass-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 10l4.553-2.277A1 1 0 0121 8.618v6.764a1 1 0 01-1.447.894L15 14M3 8a2 2 0 012-2h8a2 2 0 012 2v8a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V8z" />
              </svg>
            </span>
            <span class="text-white-200/70 leading-relaxed">A content system that keeps you visible on social — without you ever having to pick up a camera</span>
          </li>

          <!-- Target/funnel icon -->
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="mt-0.5 w-10 h-10 rounded-sm bg-brass-500/10 border border-brass-500/30 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brass-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" />
              </svg>
            </span>
            <span class="text-white-200/70 leading-relaxed">Campaigns and funnels built to turn attention into actual customers</span>
          </li>

          <!-- Clock icon -->
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="mt-0.5 w-10 h-10 rounded-sm bg-brass-500/10 border border-brass-500/30 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brass-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
            </span>
            <span class="text-white-200/70 leading-relaxed">A marketing presence that works for your business around the clock, so you can focus on running it</span>
          </li>

        </ul>

        <a href="#contact" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-brass-500 hover:text-brass-400 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-sm transition-colors">
          Learn More
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Photo -->
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="absolute -top-4 -left-4 w-full h-full border border-brass-500/20"></div>
        <img
          src="/images/about-photo.jpg"
          alt="Blackout Media in the field"
          class="relative w-full aspect-[4/5] object-cover"
        />
        <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-1/3 bg-gradient-to-t from-black-950/80 to-transparent"></div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
